'''John Chapman''' is an actor who portrayed a [[Rebel pilot]] during the briefing room and [[Royal Award Ceremony|medal ceremony]] scenes of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. Chapman refers to his character as "Gil 'Drifter' Viray" on his website, and assigns him the callsign "[[Red Twelve]]." However, no official publications identify his character, and ''[[The Essential Guide to Warfare]]'' gives the Red Twelve callsign to [[Puck Naeco]].

